#: addons/Coastal_Mountainsides.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10 standard
msgid "Coastal Mountainsides"
msgstr "Côtiers de montagne"

#: addons/Coastal_Mountainsides.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Four empires head face-to-face, surrounded by two large seas. Along with "
"mountains acting like natural walls, which cannot be crossed at all. "
"However, there is one land bridge that connects the large seas, giving the "
"empires a solution, and the only solution to conquer the whole area."
msgstr ""
"Quatre empires se font face, entourés de deux grandes mers. Ainsi que des "
"montagnes qui agissent comme des murs naturels, qu’il est absolument "
"impossible de franchir. Cependant, il y a un pont terrestre qui relie les "
"grandes mers, donnant aux empires une solution, et la seule solution pour "
"conquérir toute la région."

